item.title: CVE-2021-24681|2024-08-03T19:42:16.052Z -- unknown -- duplicate%20page
item.description: The Duplicate Page WordPress plugin through 4.4.2 does not sanitise or escape the Duplicate Post Suffix settings before outputting it, which could allow high privilege users to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
